{"tid":1997172,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"他怎麼了 - 蔣芸","createTime":"2020-05-01T12:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T12:54:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"da2a18aaabdc9b326977691cc31bbc656b6ebd03","tid":1997172,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:54:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E8%94%A3%E8%8A%B8/daily/article/20200501/20910039/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E8%2594%25A3%25E8%258A%25B8%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200501%2F20910039%2F&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw14Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=b30db076\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E8%2594%25A3%25E8%258A%25B8%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200501%2F20910039%2F&h=2aa5e998\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E8%94%A3%E8%8A%B8/daily/article/20200501/20910039/</a><br />\n<br />\n他怎麼了 - 蔣芸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200501/large/1588238004_5c3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200501%2Flarge%2F1588238004_5c3b.jpg&h=596ba5a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n區院法官郭偉健判案時，大篇幅的譴責反修例示威中的暴力行為，暴露了身為法官者偏頗心態；雖說他不是那位手持利刃連傷了三位年輕人的導遊，但把行兇者的暴力行為美化，把所作所為說成情有可原。判案顯露出的是一種法庭暴力，有大律師評法官庭上的言論「奇怪」，會影響到公眾對法庭的觀感。<br />\n<br />\n就這樣算了。。。。。。。。。針對的眼，閉的是縱容的眼，身受其害的黃店投訴無門徒呼奈何。<br />\n<br />\n好了，現在又出現了這一宗聳人聽聞的法庭判決，我們無法不將。。。。。。。。。。而三的破壞到幾乎蕩然無存，請問還能相信什麼？<br />\n<br />\n被美化的兇徒具有高尚情操之說已令人駭異，庭上的法官如此放。。。。。。。。。。。人的「高尚情操」，二十年後，為殺人兇徒而強做解人，太奇怪了。 <br />\n<br />\n蔣芸<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}